# No Backend in This App

**Do not add backend code here.**

All backend logic, APIs, and server-side code must be written only in **`selorg-dashboard-backend-v1.1/`** (at the workspace root).

This app (rider_app) is frontend/client only. Call backend via the APIs exposed by `selorg-dashboard-backend-v1.1/`.
